title: Sort Me! The Game 1.0.2 Android
description:
In Sort Me! The Game your objective is to sort the numbers on the hive from the lowest on the top to the highest on the bottom.
Take your time. No need to hurry. There are no timers counting down and no tries limit - it's great for you to keep your mind exercised and relax at the same time.

There are 3 hives to sort - 6, 10 and 15 pieces, and each time you start a game, new numbers will show up.

======================================

To install, copy the APK to your device, enable unknown sources and run the APK.

ENJOY
